***Detailed Steel Bunker Prefab***
Made by akMan
Orbital Studio

Feel free to use this prefab in your map.
This prefab includes:
-a working door
-light
-breakable wood
-sound effects
-cover (crate, table...ect)
*INSTALLATION*
unzip the file to "steamapps/USERNAME/sourcesdk/bin/prefabs"

**Please favorite this prefab if you like it. Thanks.
Enjoy!
-akMan
